@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> November 2025</p>

<p>
    Interport Cargo (“we,” “our,” or “us”) is committed to protecting the privacy of our customers and users (“you”).
    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our website and related services.
</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Account information</strong> – your name, email address, and contact details when you register or log in.</li>
    <li><strong>Quotation data</strong> – details entered in quotation requests (source, destination, package type, containers, notes).</li>
    <li><strong>Usage data</strong> – browser details, IP address, and session information to improve performance and security.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Create and manage your account</li>
    <li>Process and manage quotation requests</li>
    <li>Communicate updates or changes related to your requests</li>
    <li>Improve the functionality and security of the website</li>
</ul>
<p>We will <strong>not</strong> sell or rent your personal information to third parties.</p>

<h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
<p>
    We store data securely using industry-standard protections and take reasonable steps to prevent unauthorised access, misuse, or loss.
</p>

<h2>4. Cookies and Sessions</h2>
<p>
    We use cookies and session data to keep you logged in and to manage quotation requests. Disabling cookies may affect site functionality.
</p>

<h2>5. Access and Correction</h2>
<p>
    You may access, update, or request deletion of your personal information by logging into your account or contacting us.
</p>

<h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>
    Where we use third-party services (e.g. hosting, email, analytics), they are expected to follow privacy standards comparable to this policy.
</p>

<h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date.
</p>

<h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
<p>
    If you have any questions about this policy, contact us at:
    <a href="mailto:privacy@interportcargo.com">privacy@interportcargo.com</a>
</p>
